# Accountant Duck
Small application to track and register deposits and expenses of money and see the final balance.

# Login [POST /login]
Used to login in the app.

Receives a JSON object called user with name and password.

+ Parameters
    + name (string, required) - The user name.
    + password (string, required) - The password for the user.

+ Request (application/json)

    + Body

            {
              "user": {
                "name": "USERNAME",
                "password": "PASSWORD"
              }
            }

+ Response 200 (application/json)

    + Body

            {
              "name": "USERNAME",
              "password": "0be64ae89ddd24e225434de95d501711339baeee18f009ba9b4369af27d30d60"
            }

# Logout [GET /logout]
Used to logout in the app.

+ Response 204

