### Movement Create [POST]
+ Attributes
    + description (string, required) - The description of the movement.
    + price (string, required) - The amount of the transaction.
    + type (string, required) - The type of the movement.
    + created_at (string, required) - The date of the transaction.

+ Request (application/json)

    + Body

            {
              "movement": {
                "description": "initial balance",
                "price": "1400",
                "type": "Deposit",
                "created_at": 2015-09-01"
              }
            }

+ Response 201 (application/json)

    + Body

            {
              "description": "initial balance",
              "price": "1400",
              "type": "Deposit",
              "created_at": 2015-09-01",
              "id": "1"
            }

## Movement [/movements/{id}]
Actions on the id resource.

+ Parameters
    + id (number, required) - Movement id.

### Movement Show [GET]

+ Response 200 (application/json)

    + Body

            {
